{"title":"致拉丁美洲","authors":["袁水拍"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":8,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致拉丁美洲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁水拍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是拉丁美洲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香蕉园，甘蔗田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾森豪威尔的后院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"殖民地人民的牢监！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是拉丁美洲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硝石矿，黄铜矿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义的血库粮仓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族独立的绞刑场！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉丁美洲啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁链把你锁得紧紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是，你两眼怒睁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！熔岩一定要喷出地层！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉丁美洲啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在地球那一边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在地球这一边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背脊贴着背脊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国感到了你的呼吸！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}